'''安康圣母圣殿'''（Basilica of Our Lady of Health）位于印度卡纳塔克邦達文蓋雷县[[哈里哈尔|哈里哈尔]]，是一个圣母朝圣中心。

不分种姓、语言和宗教的人都经常造访该堂。<ref name=iubilaeummisericordiae>{{Cite web|url=http://www.giubileodellamisericordia.va/content/gdm/pt/mondo/porte-della-misericordia.html|title=Portas da Misericórdia|website=www.giubileodellamisericordia.va|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118013157/http://www.giubileodellamisericordia.va/content/gdm/pt/mondo/porte-della-misericordia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在8月至9月的庆祝活动期间，成千上万的朝圣者来到该堂。该堂的庆日是9月8日圣母圣诞瞻礼.2018年，20万名信徒参加了节日庆祝<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newskarnataka.com/davangere/3-lakh-devotees-flock-to-the-shrine-of-our-lady-of-health-harihar|title=2 lakh devotees flock to the Shrine of Our Lady of Health, Harihar|website=NewsKarnataka|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021172354/https://www.newskarnataka.com/davangere/3-lakh-devotees-flock-to-the-shrine-of-our-lady-of-health-harihar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==历史==
基督教在卡纳塔克邦有着悠久的历史。该堂的历史可追溯到18世纪。1992年8月31日，建造了一座献给安康圣母的新教堂。2012年5月27日，该堂正式宣布为[[天主教希莫加教区|天主教希莫加教区]]的教区朝圣地<ref name=iubilaeummisericordiae />。

2019年9月18日，梵蒂冈将哈里哈尔安康圣母堂升格为宗座圣殿。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.daijiworld.com/news/newsDisplay.aspx?newsID=631725|title=Shivamogga: Our Lady of Health Church Harihar declared Minor Basilica|website=www.daijiworld.com|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211054045/http://www.daijiworld.com/news/newsDisplay.aspx%3FnewsID%3D631725|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.catholictime.com/shivamogga/5061-holy-see-declares-shrine-of-our-our-lady-of-health-harihar-as-minor-basilica|title=Holy See declares Shrine of Our Our Lady of Health, Harihar as Minor Basilica|website=CATHOLICTIME.COM|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021172353/https://www.catholictime.com/shivamogga/5061-holy-see-declares-shrine-of-our-our-lady-of-health-harihar-as-minor-basilica|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这是卡纳塔克邦的第三座宗座圣殿，仅次于班加罗尔总教区的[[圣母圣殿_(班加罗尔)|圣母圣殿]]，和乌杜皮教区的[[圣老楞佐圣殿_(卡尔卡拉)|圣老楞佐圣殿]]。正式庆祝活动于2020年1月15日举行<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mangalorean.com/pope-francis-elevates-shrine-of-our-lady-of-health-harihar-to-minor-basilica/|title=Pope Francis elevates Shrine of Our Lady of Health, Harihar to Minor Basilica|first1=Michael|last1=Rodrigues|first2=Team|last2=Mangalorean|date=6 October 2019|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021172354/https://www.mangalorean.com/pope-francis-elevates-shrine-of-our-lady-of-health-harihar-to-minor-basilica/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

